.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BA136D1FFAB765BFF3AD2494F6CF4F4" blockId="118.[145,762,1553,1882]" lastBlockId="118.[809,1426,197,495]" pageId="118" pageNumber="535">
<emphasis id="B96AEAC3FFAB765BFF3AD2494B34F33C" box="[145,256,1553,1574]" italics="true" pageId="118" pageNumber="535">Remarks:</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EF8F4B20FFAB765BFEBCD2494837F33D" author="Buckle D &amp; Carroll D &amp; Crawford R &amp; Roth V" box="[279,515,1553,1575]" pageId="118" pageNumber="535" pagination="89 - 191" refId="ref89563" refString="Buckle D, Carroll D, Crawford R, Roth V. 2001. Linyphiidae and Pimoidae of America north of Mexico: checklist, synonymy, and literature. Fabreries, Supplement 10: 89 - 191." type="journal article" year="2001">
